lead_paragraph: Rio-bound U.S. Olympian Sandi Morris soared to the highest outdoor pole vault in the world this year when she cleared 4.93 meters at Houston on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: American Morris Soars to Year's Top Outdoor Pole Vault
